data.description: Well built brick home on .83 acres in beautiful North Florida! The home was renovated in 2022 with quartz countertops, freshly painted cabinets, new paint inside and out, wood windows reglazed and painted, wood laminate flooring throughout, new appliances, and all new light fixtures. Other updates include two new AC units in 2019, roof replaced in 2018, newer water heaters. Perfect for entertaining, the home offers a spacious kitchen open to the dining and just off the living room. The expansive laundry room is sure to make doing your laundry a bit more enjoyable. Enjoy the outdoors from the large screened back porch or the covered front porch. Jasper FL is located just 30 mins south of Valdosta GA, an hour from Gainesville and convenient drives to Jacksonville and Tallahassee. Enjoy small town, country living with easy access to many major cities and beaches!
